{"tid":998302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國買家大撤退　日房地產交易大減逾3成","createTime":"2019-01-28T00:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T16:51:01.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"660b17211e158c415e276b2921244bbfec518226","tid":998302,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:51:21.000Z","msg":"2018下半年日本房地產交易大減3分之1，反映外國人收購日本不動產的風氣大幅降溫。<br />\n <br />\n根據都市未來總合研究所數據，去年12月止的6個月日本房地產交易比1年前減少34%至1.72兆日圓，是6年來最低，其中外國人貢獻的交易狂減90%至919億日圓；外國人1年前貢獻逾3成總交易。<br />\n <br />\n相較於其他市場的房地產，日本不動產具吸引力，原因是價格相對較低，但情況如今已改觀。1名美國不動產基金日本部門主管說：「我們最近一直無法大量收購房地產。」這名主管指出，2018下半年日本市場房地產數量開始減少，正在尋找買家的房地產價格則太高。<br />\n <br />\n日本房地產交易降溫的現象在高階市場特別明顯。1個投資人集團去年以約1500億日圓價碼買下東京港區芝公園大樓，寫下去年最高房地產成交金額（不含開發用地），但這個數字遠低於2017年。"},{"pid":"e38df8ecbf82351e1f84019c8ff487724cdca43e","tid":998302,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:53:42.000Z","msg":"中國人回歸發展  又贏"},{"pid":"dd6eae219657ba5d7f735bd9b068f2a7f4bc12ef","tid":998302,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:55:08.000Z","msg":"燎原火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/next-photos/NextMag/1266/640pixfolder/B1266_018_japan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FNextMag%2F1266%2F640pixfolder%2FB1266_018_japan.jpg&h=2c87b5dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6143a97f893b164541919932d71ddd6788325439","tid":998302,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd6eae219657ba5d7f735bd9b068f2a7f4bc12ef","tid":998302,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T00:55:08.000Z","msg":"燎原火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/next-photos/NextMag/1266/640pixfolder/B1266_018_japan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsta